{# E1 — First-touch carrier outreach for deBoer Freight / Sofia Reyes
   Variables available:
     legal_name      : str  — carrier legal or DBA name (may be blank); DO NOT title-case
     state           : str  — carrier state abbreviation (may be blank)
     state_full      : str  — full state name (e.g. "Florida")
     equipment       : str  — human-readable equipment bucket (e.g. "dry vans and flatbeds")
     contact_name    : str  — primary contact name (may be blank); preserve casing

   Subject rotation: based on (dot_number|0) % 3
     0 -> "Introduction — deBoer Freight"
     1 -> "{{ legal_name }}: capacity question"   (or fallback if blank; preserve legal name casing)
     2 -> "Quick intro from deBoer Freight"
#}

{# ---------- SUBJECT ---------- #}
{% if subject_variant == 1 and legal_name %}
{{ legal_name }}: capacity question
{% elif subject_variant == 2 %}
Quick intro from deBoer Freight
{% else %}
Introduction -- deBoer Freight
{% endif %}

{# ---------- BODY ---------- #}
{% if contact_name %}
Hi {{ contact_name }},
{% else %}
Hi,
{% endif %}

My name is Derek deBoer, owner/operator of deBoer Freight, a licensed broker based in South Florida. We move freight regularly in and out of {{ state_full if state_full else "the Southeast" }} and we're building out our carrier network.

{% if equipment and equipment != "freight" %}
We're specifically looking for carriers running {{ equipment }} in and out of {{ state_full if state_full else "the Southeast" }}.
{% else %}
We're looking for carriers running dry vans, flatbeds, or box trucks in and out of {{ state_full if state_full else "the Southeast" }}.
{% endif %}

If you've got capacity in that region, we'd like to get you in our system. Just reply with your rate sheet or ballpark pricing on the lanes you run and we'll go from there.

Thanks,
Derek deBoer
www.deboerfreight.com
(305) 767-3480
MC 1712065
